  "difficulty": "INTERMEDIATE",
  "season": null,
  "sourceType": "SYNTHESISED",
  "sourceNotes": "Wax resist is a standard pottery decoration technique. Adapted here for no-kiln air-dry context using wax emulsion and acrylic washes.",
